Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(450,300)\c&HC1CF7A&\3c&H9FB5FE&\bord4\blur1}Sword Art Offline
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全攻略游戏的保险级别是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楼层数加上Lv.10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以爸爸他们和第1层头目战斗时是Lv.11左右
